@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUTOMATIONS MODULE - Workflow Automations
### ============================================

### WORKFLOWS - List Workflows
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/workflows?page=1&limit=20&status=active
Authorization: {{token}}

### WORKFLOWS - Get Workflow
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/workflows/:workflowId
Authorization: {{token}}

### WORKFLOWS - Create Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/automations/workflows
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lead Scoring Automation",
  "description": "Automatically score leads based on engagement",
  "triggers": [
    {
      "type": "contact_created",
      "conditions": []
    }
  ],
  "actions": [
    {
      "type": "update_field",
      "field": "score",
      "value": 50
    }
  ],
  "enabled": true
}

### WORKFLOWS - Enable/Disable Workflow
PUT {{baseUrl}}/automations/workflows/:workflowId/toggle
Authorization: {{token}}

### EXECUTIONS - List Executions
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/executions?workflowId=workflow-uuid&page=1
Authorization: {{token}}

### EXECUTIONS - Get Execution Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/executions/:executionId
Authorization: {{token}}

### TRIGGERS - List Available Triggers
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/triggers
Authorization: {{token}}

### ACTIONS - List Available Actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/actions
Authorization: {{token}}

### AI SUGGESTIONS - Get Suggestions
GET {{baseUrl}}/automations/suggestions?context=contact_engagement
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Trigger types: contact_created, deal_updated, activity_logged, etc
### - Action types: send_email, update_field, create_task, etc
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
